A reference to a dashboard item. References are stored in the preferences of each identity that uses the dashboard.

DASH_REG_MEDIUM1

public static java.lang.String DASH_REG_MEDIUM1
Column type names for a dashboard content items. These strings are used to identify which column in the dashboard layout that the DashboardContent object belongs in. These column names also map to css styles that specify width and formatting for each column.

equals

public boolean equals(java.lang.Object o)
Description copied from class: SailPointObject
We override equals so that two objects will compare equal if they have the same database id or unique name, but are different Java objects. This is necessary for Hibernate because caches commonly have to be cleared or objects from one session need to be used to match things loaded in a different session.
